      "content": "thanks. looks good. one thing though, the new model is supposed to be 20% faster but it's still pretty new and might not have the same level of nuance or personalized touch that you have. maybe add a note to the guide suggesting that if they feel the service is lacking or \"robotic\" compared to what they're used to, they should contact us immediately? just want to manage expectations in case the transition feels a bit cold.",
