      "content": "Here's an updated version of the transition guide:\n\n\"Dear valued partner,\n\nWe are excited to announce the upgrade to our backend system, which will significantly enhance your experience with our interface. Starting tomorrow morning, our system will be temporarily unavailable from midnight to accommodate the upgrade. During this time, you may experience some intermittent disruptions. Once the system is live, you can expect a refreshed user interface, improved performance, and expanded features to support your business needs.\n\nPlease note that although our new system is 20% faster, it may still learn and adapt to your business over time. If, in the short term, you find the service feels less personalized or 'robotic' than what you're used to, we encourage you to contact us. We value your feedback and are here to ensure a seamless experience for you. If there's anything specific not meeting your expectations, please don't hesitate to reach out.\n\nSincerely, [Your Name]\"",
